Privacy Policy for Masera-Tech App

1. Introduction

Welcome to the Masera-Tech App, provided by ALMASERA FOR ENGINEERING PRODUCTION. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and safeguard your information. By using the Masera-Tech App, you agree to the terms outlined in this policy.

2. Information Collected
To enhance the overall user experience and facilitate user requests, we collect the following details: User Name, User ID, and Password. The collected information is securely hashed within the same OS file, ensuring its safety.


3. Use of Collected Data
We use the collected data solely for the following purposes:
Enabling users to complete their requests
Improving user experience

4. Data Storage and Security
All user data is hashed on the same device and is not transmitted or stored elsewhere. We take measures to ensure the security and protection of user data.

5. Permissions
The Masera-Tech App may request certain permissions for features such as camera, location, etc. These permissions are solely used for the intended functionalities of the app and are not shared with third parties.


6. Location
This app requests location permission only when the user checks in or out on the attendance screen. It compares the employee's location with the admin-set work location. If inside, a success notification appears; otherwise, an alert indicates being outside the designated area. Importantly, no location data is stored or shared.

7. Third-Party Services
We do not use third-party services or SDKs in the Masera-Tech App.

8. Analytics
We do not use analytics services.

9. Age Requirement
The Masera-Tech App is intended for individuals employed, with an age requirement of 18 years and above.

10. Opt-Out Options
Users can opt-out by contacting the admin of the company, the HR department, or through direct communication with the Masera-Tech App support team via email at development@masera.jo.

11. Important Data Handling
We securely handle important data for transactions, navigation between pages, and services within the app.

12. Updates to Privacy Policy
We reserve the right to update this Privacy Policy. Users will be notified of any changes through the app or other communication channels.

Contact Information

If you have any questions or concerns regarding this Privacy Policy, please contact us at development@masera.jo.

Legal Entity

ALMASERA FOR ENGINEERING PRODUCTION
Trading as: Masera-Tech
Location: Jordan, Amman, Alwaha St.

Effective Date: 2024-01-27
